 predicts a non-monotonous\ndependence on density in semi-quantitative agreement with a recent experimental\nstudy [cf. Hubert {\\it et al.}, Phys. Rev. {\\bf X}9, 021026 (2019)].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2019 09:47:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Oct 2019 14:20:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 22 Oct 2019 10:04:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-29"}
